{"title":"故乡的池塘","authors":["阎墨林"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":10,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的池塘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎墨林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的池塘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嵌在我记忆中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神奇的镜框"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今　你还珍藏着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那幅水墨画么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆娑的树影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一团团欢乐的云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂抹在层次分明的宣纸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落雨的黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又和诗一般的情调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把青绿的田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渲染成一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望不透的苍茫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清凉凉的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷醉了一个甜蜜的村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温馨的想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向故乡的池塘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即便是没有相见吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一片实实在在的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也会在我心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时刻刻地生长……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}